hello 
please check the link "http://fresherschallenge.herokuapp.com/" to get the project hosted in heroku .



in the home page it is 3 drop down boxes . you can check any drop down box by selecting in the given drop down box.

if you select any one you will directly enter the show page for the category or subcategory or sub-sub-category.

you can view the list of all the category ,sub-category or sub-sub-category in the index page.

in the category show page alse you can able to select the sub category and directly check there.

you can add category or suncategory or sub-sub-category in the details index pages .there is a link to add new respective category .  

              
  you can check  the detailed coding in the github in the repository.